Jasmine Rice has a natural fragrance in itself, especially when cooked. Also it is famous for its unique appearance, texture and aroma.Jasmine Rice is pure white, springy and so soft to the taste at the same time.

 

Specification of Jasmine Rice

Description Jasmine Rice Standard
Purity 92% min
Moisture 14% max
Whole Kernels 60% min
Broken (5.2 mm.) 4.5% max
Red kernels  0%
Yellow kernels 0.2% max
Chalky kernels  6% max
Damaged kernels 0.25% max
White Glutinous Rice 1.5% max
Undeveloped, Immature kernels, Other seeds and Foreign Matter 0.2% max
Paddy (grain per 1 kg.) 7 grains
Milling Degree Extra Well Milled
